videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe WR breaks out for big gain
videos.description: Markis McCray springs to the left  for a 37-yard gain.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe QB rushes for games' 1st TD
videos.description: Caleb Evans rushes up the middle for a 7-yard touchdown in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe extends lead with safety
videos.description: S Nick Ingram sacks QB Jordan Davis in the end zone for a safety.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe QB rushes for 2nd TD
videos.description: QB Caleb Evans takes the option play to the right for a 38-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisiana RB barrels through for TD
videos.description: RB Elijah Mitchell rushes up the middle for a one-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisiana RB rushes for 2nd TD
videos.description: RB Elijah Mitchell bounces to the right for a 10-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe QB strikes for long gain
videos.description: QB Caleb Evans completes a big pass to RB Derrick Gore for a 46-yard gain.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe QB rushes for 3rd TD
videos.description: QB Caleb Evans rushes to the right for a seven-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisiana QB rushes for TD
videos.description: Dion Ray breaks out to the right for a 6-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe QB rushes for 4th TD
videos.description: QB Caleb Evans takes the option play up the middle for a five-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Evans rushes for 5th TD
videos.description: QB Caleb Evans scrambles and runs it in for a six-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Nunez finds Jackson for TD
videos.description: Louisiana QB Andre Nunez completes a pass over the middle to WR Jarrod Jackson for a 12-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Nunez connects with Bradley for huge TD to force OT
videos.description: As time expires, Louisiana QB Andre Nunez finds WR Ja'Marcus Bradley for a 14-yard touchdown to tie the game.

videos.headline: Gore rushes for game winning TD in double OT
videos.description: RB Derrick Gore breaks free up the middle for the game winning touchdown in double overtime.
